Rating: 4
I have made this many times over the past couple of years. I could eat it by the bucket. I use it almost as written. I add the whipping cream directly to the soup - enough to add just a hint of cream, but not drowning the soup in fat. The sweetness of the carrots makes all the difference, so I try to choose thinner, sweeter carrots. The times that I've screwed it up, I've added too much lemon juice or too much salt. All-in-all, it's one of my favs for an easy, tasty soup.

Rating: 4
